  "description": "A spacious, functional and fairly advanced two-chamber household refrigerator with the ability to remotely control it directly from the user's smartphone (this will require the installation of the SmartThinQ application). First of all, let's pay attention to the fact that the model is based on a reliable inverter linear compressor, thanks to which the model boasts excellent energy efficiency (corresponds to class A ++), as well as extremely quiet operation (the noise level does not exceed 36 dB). Both chambers have their own cooling circuits, thanks to which the operation of each of them can be independently controlled (including turned off). The cooling system supports Multi Air Flow technology and Door Cooling+ door cooling system. Refrigerator LG GB-B72PZDMN has a good capacity - the total usable volume is 384 liters, so the model can serve as an excellent choice for a family of 3-4 people. The 277L refrigerator compartment boasts a special FRESH Balancer and FRESHConverter freshness zone, and there is also a handy shelf for bottles. The freezer for 107 liters is located below, its capacity is enough to freeze about 12 kg of food per day, there is a quick freezing function, when activated, the temperature inside the chamber drops to -24 ° C.",
